(17,25,'备忘录模式（Memento）：保存和恢复对象状态','备忘录模式在不破坏封装的前提下捕获对象内部状态以便恢复。以游戏存档和编辑器撤销为例。','# 备忘录模式（Memento Pattern）

## 意图
在不破坏封装的前提下捕获对象内部状态并外部化保存，以便以后恢复。

## 代码示例
```java
// 备忘录
public class TextMemento {
    private final String content;
    private final int cursorPos;
    public TextMemento(String content, int pos) {
        this.content = content; this.cursorPos = pos;
    }
    public String getContent() { return content; }
}

// 原发器
public class TextEditor {
    private StringBuilder content = new StringBuilder();
    private int cursorPos;

    public TextMemento save() {
        return new TextMemento(content.toString(), cursorPos);
    }

    public void restore(TextMemento memento) {
        this.content = new StringBuilder(memento.getContent());
        this.cursorPos = memento.getCursorPos();
    }
}

// 管理者
public class History {
    private Stack<TextMemento> stack = new Stack<>();
    public void push(TextMemento m) { stack.push(m); }
    public TextMemento pop() { return stack.pop(); }
}
```','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1499750310107-5fef28a66643?w=800','设计模式',NULL,0,NULL,'设计模式-17',NULL,NULL,0,'PUBLISHED',1548,106,16,4,'2026-04-03 00:26:11','2025-12-02 04:46:11','2025-12-02 04:46:11',NULL,0),
