## 概述
DevOps 通过自动化工具链打通开发和运维，实现持续集成和持续交付。

```yaml
# GitHub Actions
name: CI
on:
  push:
    branches: [main]
jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - name: Build
        run: |
          mvn clean package
      - name: Deploy
        run: |
          scp target/app.jar user@server:/app/
          ssh user@server ''systemctl restart myapp''
```
